Method Detail

onVenueInfoFetched

void onVenueInfoFetched(java.util.List<VenueInfo> venues)
Called when AcceleratorClient.fetchVenueInfo(java.util.List, com.skyhookwireless.accelerator.AcceleratorClient.VenueInfoListener) or AcceleratorClient.fetchVenueInfoAtLocation(com.skyhookwireless.accelerator.AcceleratorClient.VenueInfoListener) completes successfully.

If there was an error, then this method will not be called, and the onVenueInfoError(int) method will be called instead.

Parameters:
venues - list of venue information. IDs that are not valid or for which there is no information will be omitted from the list.

onVenueInfoError

void onVenueInfoError(int errorCode)
Called when an error occurs when fetching venue information.

This method will be called only if an error occurred.

Parameters:
errorCode - the error code of the operation. Possible error code ERROR_UNAUTHORIZED, ERROR_SERVER_UNAVAILABLE, and for fetchVenueInfoAtLocation also ERROR_CANNOT_DETERMINE_LOCATION, ERROR_OPERATION_ABORTED. More details can be found in AcceleratorStatusCodes.
